text: tavada numbalage nives tulin numbalata sevanak allah numbalata æti kaleya. tavada numbala gaman biman yana dinaka ho numbala nævati sitina dinaka eya (rægena yamata) numbalata pahasu vana nives govipala satunge samin numbalata æti kaleya. tavada unge lom unge ham ha unge roma valin bhanda ha mada kalakata bhukti vindimak da (æti kaleya)
